3 32 32 32h384c17.67 0 32-14.33 32-32v-32c0-17.67-14.33-32-32-32z\"><\/path><\/svg><\/span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<a class=\"elementor-accordion-title\" tabindex=\"0\">\u00bfQu\u00e9 seguridad tengo sobre mis productos y mi dinero?<\/a>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"elementor-tab-content-1752\" class=\"elementor-tab-content elementor-clearfix\" data-tab=\"2\" role=\"region\" aria-labelledby=\"elementor-tab-title-1752\"><p data-path-to-node=\"4\"><span data-path-to-node=\"4,1\"><span class=\"citation-186\">Tus productos viajan protegidos con un <\/span><b data-path-to-node=\"4,1\" data-index-in-node=\"39\"><span class=\"citation-186\">seguro gratuito<\/span><\/b><span class=\"citation-186\"> que cubre robo, p\u00e9rdida o da\u00f1os materiales hasta por S\/ 300.00<\/span><\/span><span data-path-to-node=\"4,3\">. <\/span><span data-path-to-node=\"4,5\"><span class=\"citation-185\">Adem\u00e1s, garantizamos tu liquidez realizando el dep\u00f3sito de tus ventas cobradas mediante contra entrega el mismo d\u00eda<\/span><\/span><span data-path-to-node=\"4,7\">.<\/span><\/p><\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-accordion-item\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"elementor-tab-title-1753\" class=\"elementor-tab-title\" data-tab=\"3\" role=\"button\" aria-controls=\"elementor-tab-content-1753\" aria-expanded=\"false\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-accordion-icon elementor-accordion-icon-right\" aria-hidden=\"true\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-accordion-icon-closed\"><svg class=\"e-font-icon-svg e-fas-plus\" viewBox=\"0 0 448 512\" xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\"><path d=\"M416 208H272V64c0-17.67-14.33-32-32-32h-32c-17.67 0-32 14.33-32 32v144H32c-17.67 0-32 14.33-32 32v32c0 17.67 14.33 32 32 32h144v144c0 17.67 14.33 32 32 32h32c17.67 0 32-14.33 32-32V304h144c17.67 0 32-14.33 32-32v-32c0-17.67-14.33-32-32-32z\"><\/path><\/svg><\/span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-accordion-icon-opened\"><svg class=\"e-font-icon-svg e-fas-minus\" viewBox=\"0 0 448 512\" xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\"><path d=\"M416 208H32c-17.67 0-32 14.33-32 32v32c0 17.67 14.33 32 32 32h384c17.67 0 32-14.33 32-32v-32c0-17.67-14.33-32-32-32z\"><\/path><\/svg><\/span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<a class=\"elementor-accordion-title\" tabindex=\"0\">\u00bfC\u00f3mo funciona la log\u00edstica de recojo y entrega?<\/a>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"elementor-tab-content-1753\" class=\"elementor-tab-content elementor-clearfix\" data-tab=\"3\" role=\"region\" aria-labelledby=\"elementor-tab-title-1753\"><p data-path-to-node=\"6\"><span data-path-to-node=\"6,1\"><span class=\"citation-184\">Solo debes solicitarlo antes de las 9:30 am para que recojamos tu mercader\u00eda entre las 10:00 am y 12:30 pm<\/span><\/span><span data-path-to-node=\"6,3\">. <\/span><span data-path-to-node=\"6,5\"><span class=\"citation-183\">Las entregas se realizan esa misma tarde, en un rango de 2:00 pm a 7:30 pm, envi\u00e1ndote una foto como respaldo de cada entrega exitosa<\/span><\/span><span data-path-to-node=\"6,7\">.<\/span><\/p><\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-27a94fe e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"27a94fe\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-54e388e elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"54e388e\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img width=\"1024\" height=\"1024\" src=\"https:\/\/mercourier.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/02\/WhatsApp-Image-2026-02-20-at-7.17.17-PM-2.jpeg\" class=\"attachment-large size-large wp-image-6496\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/mercourier.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/02\/WhatsApp-Image-2026-02-20-at-7.17.17-PM-2.jpeg 1024w, https: